> I shall have a look at otags, which, being built
> with camlp4 support, ought to be parametrizable (?).

Sure, use option -pa :

$ otags -help
Available commands:
  [...
  -pa <str>      add camlp4 parser (default: pa_o.cmo; pa_op.cmo)

